---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Hero from "../../components/Hero.astro";
import StickyHeader from "../../components/StickyHeader.astro";
---

<Layout title="Data Protection — Rusty Notebooks">
    <StickyHeader href="/" label="Rusty Notebooks" scrollTitle="Data Protection"/>
    <div class="chapter-bg" style="--bg-image: url('/images/index.png');">
        <div class="chapter-content container">
            <Hero eyebrow="Return" title="Data Protection" />

            <section class="section section-narrative">
                <div class="narrative">
                    <p><strong>Data Protection</strong></p>

                    <p>
                        This website is operated as a personal music project.
                        Protecting your personal data is important.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Personal data is processed only to the extent necessary
                        to provide a functional and secure website.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Responsible Party</strong><br />
                        Björn Hinnah<br />
                        Address: upon request<br />
                        Email: btwentyfive@web.de
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Hosting</strong><br />
                        This website is hosted via Cloudflare Pages (Cloudflare, Inc.,
                        101 Townsend St., San Francisco, CA 94107, USA).
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        When visiting the site, technical data (such as IP
                        address, browser type, and access time) may be processed
                        automatically to ensure stability and security.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Data processing is based on Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR
                        (legitimate interest in secure and efficient operation
                        of the website). Data may be transferred to third
                        countries (e.g., USA) in accordance with applicable data
                        protection safeguards.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Web Analytics</strong><br />
                        This website does not currently use any web analytics services.
                    </p>

                    <!-- <p>
                        According to Cloudflare, this service operates without
                        cookies and does not use client-side storage such as
                        localStorage or sessionStorage.
                    </p> -->

                    <p>
                        The processing is based on Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate
                        interest in analyzing and improving website
                        performance). The collected information is used only to
                        understand website traffic and improve performance.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Embedded Content (YouTube)</strong><br />
                        This website includes embedded videos from YouTube (Google
                        Ireland Limited, Gordon House, Barrow Street, Dublin 4, Ireland).
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Videos are embedded using YouTube's privacy-enhanced
                        mode (youtube-nocookie). When interacting with these
                        videos, personal data may be transmitted to YouTube,
                        such as your IP address and usage data. Data processing
                        may also take place outside the European Union.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <strong>External Links</strong><br />
                        This website contains links to external platforms including
                        Spotify, Apple Music, YouTube, Instagram, TikTok, and DistroKid
                        / HyperFollow.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        When clicking these links, you will be redirected to the
                        respective external provider, where their own privacy
                        policies apply.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Music Distribution</strong><br />
                        Music published under the project "Rusty Notebooks" is distributed
                        via third-party services (e.g., DistroKid) and made available
                        on streaming platforms.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        We have no influence over the data processing performed
                        by these platforms.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Data Retention</strong><br />
                        Personal data is stored only for as long as necessary to fulfill
                        the purposes stated above or as required by applicable laws.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Your Rights</strong><br />
                        You have the right to:
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        – request information about your stored data<br />
                        – request correction or deletion of your data<br />
                        – request restriction of processing<br />
                        – request data portability<br />
                        – object to data processing
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        If you have any questions regarding data protection, you
                        can contact the responsible party at any time.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Right to Lodge a Complaint</strong><br />
                        You have the right to lodge a complaint with a data protection
                        supervisory authority.
                    </p>

                    <p class="narrative-final">
                        This site is built to share music — nothing more,
                        nothing hidden.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <!-- chapter-content -->
        </div>
        <!-- chapter-bg -->
    </div></Layout
>
